1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,883
WindWalker is a GPT-powered web app builder
for small businesses.

2
00:00:11,883 --> 00:00:31,230
A user describes the business they want to run: an English digital-content bookstore
with member login, carts, test checkout, purchase history, downloads, and a seller dashboard.

3
00:00:31,230 --> 00:00:56,240
WindWalker turns that request into a workflow pattern, generates a responsive preview,
and lets the user refine it through conversation before deployment to Cloudflare Pages.

4
00:00:56,240 --> 00:01:23,309
In this demo, the deployed bookstore supports mock member login, product browsing,
cart interaction, and test checkout. The same workflow adapts to bookings and customer operations.

5
00:01:23,309 --> 00:01:32,709
We used GPT-5.6 for final iteration and validation,
with OpenAI Codex supporting implementation, testing, and submission evidence.

6
00:01:32,709 --> 00:01:42,742
GPT can generate an app. WindWalker helps small-business owners launch, operate, fix,
and continuously improve it with workflow patterns and lightweight human support.
